Introduction

FALLANC was a four-member boy pop rock band under RF Entertainment. They debuted on November 5, 2018 with their debut and only single "Never Mind".

They presumably disbanded in 2019 due to inactivity on their SNS. This was confirmed by Jihoon in an Instagram comment in 2020.
